                        <interp inst="t18381217-name-720" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN SANDERS</persName>
                  </hi>. I live with my father. On the afternoon of the 12th of December, I was in the parlour, and saw the prisoner in the shop—he pulled the till under his arm and ran out—I followed, and he was taken in my presence—the money stated was all found in the till on the prisoner.</p>
