               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I was walking up the Colonnade, a boy with a black apron gave the till to me, and said it was his—they <hi rend="italic">sung out</hi>"Stop thief," and I put it down and ran away.</p>
